[DhtmlXQ_comment0]eg xqsycj tjm 233 1r1tp1a pw 1r1tp 01||第233局 车低兵士巧胜车卒（一）||Two examples discussing this scenario will be presented.||For red to win, the following must be done:||a) the red king must be used to limit the movement of the black king and pawn||b) the red king and chariot must obtain control of the central file||c) red must try to prevent the black chariot and pawn from helping each other.[/DhtmlXQ_comment0]
[DhtmlXQ_comment5]This is the key to winning, as it would force the the black chariot to give up control of the central file.[/DhtmlXQ_comment5]
